B.CX=new A.X(B.h5,["Language","English","\u0939\u093f\u0928\u094d\u0926\u0940","\u09ac\u09be\u0982\u09b2\u09be","\u0c95\u0ca8\u0ccd\u0ca8\u0ca1","\u0ba4\u0bae\u0bbf\u0bb4\u0bcd","Theme","Light Mode","Dark Mode","Color Palette","Electric Blue","Neon Purple","Emerald Green","Sunset Orange","Hot Pink","Cyber Teal","Crimson Red","Golden Amber","Home","About","Skills","Experience","Projects","Education","Contact","Resume","Hello, I'm","Avijit Dutta","Senior Mobile Developer","Flutter Engineer","Android Specialist","iOS App Publisher","AI-Assisted Developer","Android \xb7 iOS \xb7 Web (PWA) \xb7 Tablet \u2014 5 yrs in mobile \xb7 22 apps \xb7 190K+ downloads \xb7 7,500+ live devices across multiple Indian states.","Midnapore, West Bengal, India","Available for Remote Work","Download CV","Get in Touch","Scroll to explore","About Me","Who I Am","Passionate Mobile Engineer Building at Government Scale","I'm a Senior Mobile Application Developer \u2014 5 years hands-on in Android (Java/Kotlin) and Flutter (Dart), shipping cross-platform apps that run on Android, iOS, Web (PWA) and tablet form factors from a single shared codebase. 8+ years across IT, 10-year professional career, with apps live on both Play Store and App Store.","My current focus is on flavor-based, multi-tenant Flutter applications for government metering solutions, serving 7,500+ active devices across multiple Indian states. I leverage AI-assisted development with Claude, Cursor, and GitHub Copilot to ship faster without sacrificing quality.","My preferred stack is Clean MVVM + Riverpod for Flutter and MVVM + Kotlin Coroutines/Flow for native Android. Strong working knowledge of Retrofit, Room, REST APIs, WebSockets, Firebase suite, BillDesk and Razorpay integrations \u2014 plus production experience with legacy Provider/GetX codebases that I actively refactor toward modern patterns.","These last few months I've been shipping in public \u2014 open-sourcing flavor_config (a multi-tenant Dart package), widget-gallery (41 reusable Flutter + Jetpack Compose components) and this portfolio \u2014 while talking to teams about my next role.","Working Years","Mobile Dev Years","Apps Shipped","Devices Managed","Total Downloads","Skills & Tech Stack","My Toolkit","Technologies I work with daily","Programming Languages","Mobile Development","Architecture & Practices","State Management","Version Control","AI-Assisted Tools","Work Experience","My Journey","8+ years across mobile, software & engineering","Featured Projects","My Work","Apps shipped to millions of users","All","Government","Enterprise","Fintech","E-commerce","Play Store","App Store","Learn more","downloads","The Challenge","Impact","Key Features","Deployments","One Flutter codebase, many flavors","Standalone","SDK / .aar","on Play Store","on App Store","SDK partners","Visit","OPEN SOURCE","Building in public on GitHub","repos","followers","View my GitHub","WRITING","Thoughts & devlogs","ON LINKEDIN","Backed by former leadership","REMOTE READY","Set up to ship from day one","Education","Academic Background","Continuous learning, formal & online","Certifications","Let's Build Something Together","Get in Touch","Open to remote opportunities","Have a project in mind? I'd love to hear from you. Drop me an email or reach out on LinkedIn.","Your Name","Your Email","Your Message","Send Message","Email","Phone","Location","LinkedIn","Copied to clipboard","Sending\u2026","Message sent! I'll get back to you soon.","Could not send. Please email me directly.","Built with Flutter \u2764\ufe0f by Avijit Dutta \xb7 this site runs on Android, iOS & Web from one codebase","All rights reserved","visitors",'"Code is poetry written for machines, but read by humans."',"BEYOND CODE","Life outside the editor","Yoga","Keeps me mentally & physically stable \u2014 my way of handling coding stress.","Cooking","Experimenting in the kitchen to unwind and stay creative.","Football","My favourite sport \u2014 energy, focus and teamwork.","Riding","Royal Enfield owner & rider \u2014 long rides recharge my focus.","Copy","Menu","Portfolio inquiry from ","Visitor","Hi Avijit, I'd like to talk.","Present","months","years","Bcits Pvt Ltd","Bangalore","Android Developer","Driving the multi-tenant Flutter architecture behind 8+ state-discom meter apps \u2014 one codebase, 7,500+ live devices, 190K+ downloads. Owning the flavor strategy, release flow and AI-assisted refactors of a large legacy codebase (Claude, ChatGPT, Cursor, Grok).","PiTangent Analytics & Tech Solutions","Kolkata","Software Engineer","Designed and developed 11 mobile applications including e-commerce, CRM, farming management, and fintech. Achieved 60% increment (Apr 2022) and 20% increment (Apr 2023) for exceptional contributions.","Iconwizard Technologies Pvt Ltd","Kolkata","Trainee Android Developer","Completed professional Android training and contributed to client projects. Learned MVVM architecture, Jetpack components, and best coding practices.","Mother Dairy Fruits and Vegetables","Ranchi","Electro-Mechanical Engineer","Supported Java-based SCADA system for compressor automation in cold storage. Performed logic modification, alarm tuning, and event scripting. Transitioned to software development.","M/S MB Construction Pvt Ltd","Kharagpur","33/11kV Substation Maintenance Worker","Maintained 33/11kV substation equipment \u2014 routine inspections, switchgear operation and preventive maintenance \u2014 early in my career, before transitioning to industrial automation and then to mobile engineering."],t.w)
